# build context 排除清单（影响所有 Dockerfile 的 COPY 速度）
# 控制在尽量小的体积，docker compose build 才不会慢得离谱

# --- VCS / IDE ---
.git
.github
.vscode
.idea
.serena
.ccw
.agent
.agents

# --- 缓存 / 临时 ---
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/node_modules
**/.turbo
**/.next
**/.nuxt

# --- 运行时产物（重灾区，610MB+ 视频）---
**/.runtime
**/.venv
**/venv
**/dist
!packages/ruoyi-plus-soybean/dist
!packages/student-web/dist
**/build
**/coverage
**/target
!packages/RuoYi-Vue-Plus-5.X/**/target
data
tmp
logs
*.log

# --- 工作区杂项 ---
.workflow
_bmad-output
mocks
references
docs
images
Ux
update_video_input_card.sh
bench_video_pipeline.sh
*.png
!packages/**/*.png

# --- 环境 / 密钥 ---
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.production.example

# --- macOS ---
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# --- pnpm ---
pnpm-lock.yaml.bak
